Here $T_{su}$, $\Delta T_{su}$, $b_u$, $\Delta b_u$, $T_0$, $T{sl}$, $T_{pl}$, $\omega_{sl}$, $\delta_{sl}$, $b_l$ are constant parameters. Note that $T_{fu}$ and $T_{fl}$ are multi-valued functions, so special methods for numerical modelling of (\ref{DrillingEind}) are needed (see \citep{piiroinen2008event,Kiseleva2013J}).


